chanical\nsystems provide the information regarding particle's general and relativistic\nbehavior in such systems. Moreover, the proposed wave equations can also be\ntransformed into Schr\\\"odinger's and Dirac's equations. The interrelation of\nSchr\\\"odinger's, Dirac's and proposed equations with the universal wave\nequation is also presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2011 12:37:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-10-20"}
